    <string name="code_card_filename">gboost_engine.sh</string>
    <string name="code_card_caption">A real excerpt from the G-BOOST+ command set — runs through Shizuku, no root needed. Full list in the Device tab.</string>

    <string name="about_title">How SP NEW² actually works</string>
    <string name="about_p1">SP NEW² uses Shizuku — a legitimate system-permission bridge trusted by millions of Android users — to run optimization ADB commands directly on your device, with no bootloader unlock and no root. Everything happens quietly in the background.</string>
    <string name="about_p2">For Free Fire specifically, the app targets the three most common bottlenecks on mid-range hardware: system animations eating frame time, background processes competing for RAM, and a render resolution beyond what the GPU can comfortably push. G-BOOST+ disables unnecessary effects and prioritizes resources for the game process; SUPPORT NEW² recalculates the display resolution to match your exact hardware, cutting GPU load while keeping the image sharp.</string>
    <string name="about_p3">Every change is 100%% reversible with Factory Reset. SP NEW² never modifies system files, never requests more permission than it needs, and never collects your personal data.</string>

